window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When Logan Anders was asked to be the savior of a fairy race, he’d thought there was only one….</b><br> <br> Now, he’s found himself in a new realm with a whole new species of fairies to breed and save, except this time, it isn’t as simple as rebuilding a few houses. <br> <br> Turns out that when catgirl fairies are in heat…things get intense, to say the least.<br> <br> Especially since the jungle is teeming with creatures that want nothing more than to tear them all limb from limb.</p>"; 
